                  <p class="text-sm font-black text-slate-900">$12,000</p>
                  <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mt-1">+ 6 weeks</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 mt-2 italic">â†’ AI builders + integrations handle booking, payments, user accounts, CRM integration.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Final Verdict -->
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-800 to-slate-900 text-white rounded-lg p-5">
            <p class="font-black text-lg mb-2">ðŸŽ¯ THE VERDICT:</p>
